ice De Avenel, tinha 18 anos. Ele casou-se com Margaret de Stockport em 1210, em Shipbrook, Cheshire, Inglaterra, United Kingdom. Eles tiveram pelo menos 1 filho. Em 1229, sua profissão aparece como chief justice of cheshire . Ele faleceu em 1235, em sua cidade natal, com 62 anos."},"ro":{"1173–1235":"1173–1235","1168–Male":"1168–Decedat","1170–Male":"1170–Decedat","1178–1247":"1178–1247","1186–1236":"1186–1236","1192–1237":"1192–1237","1237–1321":"1237–1321","1155–1196":"1155–1196","1155–1188":"1155–1188","1231":"1231","1186":"1186","1196":"1196","1173":"1173","1192":"1192","1170":"1170","1215":"1215","1237":"1237","1236":"1236","1247":"1247","1235":"1235","1224":"1224","1168":"1168","1321":"1321","1178":"1178","1188":"1188","1210":"1210","1155":"1155","after 1196":"după 1196","Between 1229 and 1236":"din 1229 până în 1236","Cheshire, England":"Cheshire, England","Shipbrook, Cheshire, England":"Shipbrook, Cheshire, England","Shipbrook, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"Shipbrook, Cheshire, Anglia, United Kingdom","Derby, Derbyshire, England":"Derby, Derbyshire, Anglia, United Kingdom","Shipbrook Cheshire":"Shipbrook, Cheshire, Anglia, United Kingdom"},"ru":{"1173–1235":"1173г.–1235г.","1168–Male":"1168г.–Умерший","1170–Male":"1170г.–Умерший","1178–1247":"1178г.–1247г.","1186–1236":"1186г.–1236г.","1192–1237":"1192г.–1237г.","1237–1321":"1237г.–1321г.","1155–1196":"1155г.–1196г.","1155–1188":"1155г.–1188г.","1231":"1231 г.","1186":"1186 г.","1196":"1196 г.","1173":"1173 г.","1192":"1192 г.","1170":"1170 г.","1215":"1215 г.","1237":"1237 г.","1236":"1236 г.","1247":"1247 г.","1235":"1235 г.","1224":"1224 г.","1168":"1168 г.","1321":"1321 г.","1178":"1178 г.","1188":"1188 г.","1210":"1210 г.","1155":"1155 г.","after 1196":"после 1196 г.","Between 1229 and 1236":"с 1229 по 1236","Cheshire, England":"чешир, Англия","Shipbrook, Cheshire, England":"шипбрук, чешир, Англия","Shipbrook, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom":"шипбрук, чешир, Англия, Великобритания","Derby, Der